She showed 'em again that there could be only one end to it quick death on the sea , or slow death in Philip's prisons . 
They asked no more than to embrace death for my sake . 
Many men have prayed to me for life . 
Her chest sounded like a board as she hit it . 
I told 'em that this was no time for open war with Spain . 
If by miracle inconceivable they prevailed against Philip's fleet , Philip would hold me accountable . 
to give him up their young lives . 
