'How did you get out of it ? 'By the truth . 
I says to Master Fur Cap , as I might to you here , I says , I'll tell you something , since you seem a knowledgeable man . 
She must sail the seas , Master Dawe . 
She'll be hired to merchants for the trade . 
She'll be out in all shapes o' weathers . 
