But Mr Culpeper was quite serious . 
He told them that he was a physician astrologer a doctor who knew all about the stars as well as all about herbs for medicine . 
He said that the sun , the moon , and five Planets , called Jupiter , Mars , Mercury , Saturn , and Venus , governed everybody and everything in the world . 
If you knew their likes and dislikes , he said , you could make them cure your patient and hurt your enemy , and find out the secret causes of things . 
He talked of these five Planets as though they belonged to him , or as though he were playing long games against them . 
A rat ran between Middenboro's feet , and the old pony stamped . 
