Which brought me to a stand . 
Ahem ! 'And your sick people in the meantime ? 'Puck demanded . 
'We persuaded them on the north side of the street to lie out in Hitheram's field . 
Where the plague had taken one , or at most two , in a house , folk would not shift for fear of thieves in their absence . 
They cast away their lives to die among their goods . 
'Human nature , said Puck . 
'I've seen it time and again . 
