Briefly , he enlightened me that the plague was spread by the creatures of the Moon . 
The Moon , our Lady of ill aspect , was the offender . 
My own poor wits showed me that I , Nick Culpeper , had the people in my charge , God's good providence aiding me , and no time to lose neither . 
'I posted up the hill , and broke into Hitheram's field amongst 'em all at prayers . 
