And there's a reason for all things too , though the wise physician need not blab 'em all . 
Imprimis , or firstly , the mere sport of it , which lasted ten days , drew 'em most markedly out of their melancholy . 
I'd defy sorrowful job himself to lament or scratch while he's routing rats from a rick . 
